headline: Raymond James Acquires GreensLedge to Strengthen Capital Markets and Advisory Platform
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., October 14, 2025--Raymond James (NYSE: RJF) is deepening its capital markets capabilities through the acquisition of a majority stake in GreensLedge Holdings LLC.

headline: JPMorgan Chase & Co. (JPM) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: JPMorgan Chase & Co. (JPM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +4.97% and +3.51%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: 1 Large-Cap Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 We Ignore
summary: Large-cap stocks usually command their industries because they have the scale to drive market trends. The flip side though is that their sheer size can limit growth as expanding further becomes an increasingly challenging task.
